oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bluebird 78's - tape 7
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tape 7 of recordings of Bluebird 78 discs, featuring Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers (performers), Jean Fuselier (performer), and Joe Werner and the Ramblers (performers), performing Creole tunes from the 1930's.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers; Jean Fuselier; Joe Werner and the Ramblers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Test tones -- Memoire De Mom (Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers) -- Valse A Columbus (Jean Fuselier) -- Gueydon Two Step (Jean Fuselier) -- Ma Belle Tete Catin (Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers) -- La Malliage (Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers) -- Joe's Breakdown (Joe Werner and the Ramblers) -- La Valse De Bayou (Joe Werner and the Ramblers) -- La Vieux Two Step (Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers) -- Aux Ball Se Te Maurice (Happy Fats and his Rayne-Bo Ramblers)
